      <title>电动汽车热潮导致挪威去年排放量下降，金属产量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/norway-s-emissions-fell-last-year-on-ev-boom-metal-output-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于越来越多的电动汽车上路以及冶炼厂和金属厂产量下降，挪威的排放量去年下降了 4.7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/norway-s-emissions-fell-last-year-on-ev-boom-metal-output-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 10:15:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>长续航电动汽车的价格现在低于美国新车的平均价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/long-range-evs-now-cost-less-than-the-average-us-new-car</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“达尔文式”竞争和大量新车型的推出，帮助续航里程至少为 300 英里的电动汽车在价格平价方面再创里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/long-range-evs-now-cost-less-than-the-average-us-new-car</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 10:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
