      <title>勃林格殷格翰减肥挑战者在肝脏研究中达到目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/boehringer-s-weight-loss-challenger-hits-goals-in-liver-study</link>
      <description><![CDATA[勃林格殷格翰公司和 Zealand Pharma A/S 联合研发的新一代化合物在肥胖相关肝病研究中达到了一系列目标，这初步表明该药物在快速增长的减肥市场中的竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/boehringer-s-weight-loss-challenger-hits-goals-in-liver-study</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:57:50 GMT</pubDate>
